---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Kizuna Collective Mindful Walking Circle" description="Kizuna Collective Mindful Walking Circle" />
		<style>

			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				display: flex;
				font-size: 14px;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				min-height: 100vh;

			}
			.content {
				flex-grow: 1;
				padding: 60px;
				max-width: 800px;
				width: 100%;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			.game-section {
				margin-bottom: 60px;
			}
			.game-title {
				font-size: 24px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;


			}
			
			.image-gallery {
				display: flex;
				overflow-x: auto;
				gap: 20px;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				padding-bottom: 10px;
				-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
			}
			.gallery-item {
				flex: 0 0 auto;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 533px;
				height: 300px;
			}
			.gallery-video {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
			}
			.gallery-image {
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				object-fit: cover;
			}
			.game-description {
				max-width: 600px;
				font-family: 'Geist-Regular', sans-serif;
				white-space: pre-wrap;

			}
			.game-credits {
				margin-top: 12px;
				max-width: 600px;
			}
			.game-credits ul {
				margin: 4px 0 0 0;
				padding-left: 20px;
			}
			.video-embed {
				position: relative;
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 600px;
				padding-top: 56.25%; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.video-embed iframe {
				position: absolute;
				top: 0;
				left: 0;
				width: 100%;
				height: 100%;
				border: 0;
			}
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				body {
					flex-direction: column;
				}
				.content {
					padding: 20px;
				}
				.game-title {
					font-size: 20px;
				}
				.gallery-item {
					height: 56.25vw; /* 16:9 aspect ratio */
					max-height: 300px;
				}
				.game-description {
					font-size: 14px;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Sidebar />
		<div class="content">
			<strong>Kizuna Collective Mindful Walking Workshop</strong>
			<br>
            Tokyo, Japan
            <br>
            2025
			<br>
            <hr>
            <p>I ran a weekly 6 week workshop with the Tokyo based community Kizuna Collective. They frequently run events in Tokyo to cultivate authentic and meaningful connections — or 'kizuna' (絆) </p>

            <p>One of the events they run is called Kizuna Circles which are high commitment gatherings of up to 6 people. For their third edition of Circles, I hosted a mindful walking circle/workshop with 5 participants.</p>
			<p>Each week we gathered in the early morning at a different part of Tokyo. I would facilitate a discussion for the first hour, and lead a semi structured walk for the second hour. The walks involved engaging with all our senses through various games, activities, and prompts.</p>
            <p> Notes from all 6 weeks can be read <a href="/digital-garden/mindful-walking-circle/">here</a> </p>

            <img  src="/kizuna/kizuna-poster.webp"/>

			<img  src="/kizuna/kizuna-1.webp"/>

            <img src="kizuna/walk-1.jpg"/>

            <img  src="/kizuna/kizuna-2.webp"/>

			<img  src="/kizuna/kizuna-3.webp"/>

            <img src="kizuna/walk-3.jpg"/>


			<img  src="/kizuna/kizuna-4.webp"/>

            <img  src="/kizuna/kizuna-5.webp"/>

            <img src="kizuna/walk-2.jpg"/>

            <img  src="/kizuna/kizuna-6.webp"/>

            <img  src="/kizuna/kizuna-7.webp"/>

            <img src="kizuna/walk-4.jpg"/>
    
            <img  src="/kizuna/kizuna-8.webp"/>

			<!-- <div style="width: 25%;">
			<img src="/Written-By-a-Human-Not-By-AI-Badge-white@2x.png" alt="Your Image">
			</div> -->

		</div>
	</body>
</html>